        <div class="footer-layout">
            <div class="footer-content">
                <p>Powered by the Integrated Data Service (IDS).</p>
                <p><a href="/cookies">Cookies</a></p>
                <p><img src="/images/ogl.svg" alt="OGL logo" class="ogl-logo" />All content is available under the <a href="https://www.nationalarchives.gov.uk/doc/open-government-licence/version/3/">Open Government Licence v3.0</a>, except where otherwise stated</p>
            </div>
            <div class="crown">
                <a href="https://www.nationalarchives.gov.uk/information-management/re-using-public-sector-information/uk-government-licensing-framework/crown-copyright/">
                    <img src="/images/crown.png" alt="Crown logo" />
